{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_52_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 沖縄の猫ちゃん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんのお土産何にしようかな～。せっかく\n沖縄まで来たから、沖縄！　って感じのがいいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What souvenir should I get for Suzu-nyan~ Since we came all the way\nto Okinawa‚ something that screams 'Okinawa!' would be nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3994485365,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.7333333055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "幸福の砂入りストラップに、琉球ガラス……\nおー、シーサーのグッズもいーっぱいある！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A strap filled with happy sand‚ Ryukyu glass…\nOh‚ there are tons of Shisa merchandise too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、どれも可愛いし、捨てがたいなー\nどうしようかなー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ they're all cute‚ it's hard to choose~\nWhat should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.5666670202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "随分悩んでいるみたいだな。他のみんなはお土産を\n買い終えて遊びに行ったから、ゆっくり選んでいいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem to be really struggling. Everyone else finished buying\ntheir souvenirs and went to play‚ so take your time choosing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1333336869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと！？　それじゃあさ\n{user}さんにちょっと質問してもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Well‚ then‚\nCan I ask you a question‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "シーサーってどんな子なの？　名前と\n見た目が可愛いこと以外あんまり知らないんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of creature is a Shisa? Besides the name\nand cute appearance‚ I don't really know much about them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6000054399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "悪いものが入れないようにする魔除けの役割が\nあったと思うが……あ、ほら、ここに説明書きがあるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think they have the role of warding off evil‚ preventing\nbad things from entering… Ah‚ look‚ there's an explanation here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4333387732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……「屋根の上や玄関、村の入口に置かれる\nことも多く」……へ～、凄いんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see… \"They are often placed on roofs‚ at house entrances‚\nor at village entrances\" …wow~ that's amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5333387732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それならさ、寮の玄関に置いておけば\n悪いものが寄ってこないってことだよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ if we put it at the dorm entrance‚\nbad things won't come near‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも……すずにゃんが宿題をサボったら\n悪い子だから寮に入れなくなっちゃうのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but… if Suzu-nyan skips her homework‚ and\nbecomes a bad kid‚ would she be unable to enter the dorm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はは、守り神もそこまでは厳しくないと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ I don't think the guardian deity is that strict.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.9333306352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4333286006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "そっかー。じゃあすずにゃんのお土産\nこの子達にしようっと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Then‚ for Suzu-nyan's souvenir‚\nI'll get these guys!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "どうせなら一杯お迎えした方が賑やかでいいよね\nこの子と……こっちの子も！　後は～――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm going to get them‚ better to get many to make it more lively‚ right?\nI'll get this one… and this one too! And then--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3999835689
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3999835689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、これでお土産はバッチリ\n{user}さん、手伝ってくれてありがと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ that takes care of the souvenirs.\nThank you for helping me‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "この後は自由時間だよね！　うーん、どうしようかな～\n芽衣、沖縄でやりたいことがあったはずなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have free time after this‚ right? Hmm‚ what should I do~\nMei had something she wanted to do in Okinawa‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.599995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.1999789912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ{user}さん\n芽衣、何がしたかったんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey hey‚ {user}-san\nWhat did Mei want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2946224781,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5505.373452900017,
          "startTime": 137.799995931
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは分からないが……良かったらこれを見てくれ\n橋本さんとみんなが好きそうな店は調べておいたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know about that… But if you'd like‚ take a look at this.\nI looked up stores that Hashimoto-san and everyone else might like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.299995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.8333102901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　すごーい！　ありがとう！\n芽衣達のために、こんなリストを作ってくれたんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Amazing~! Thank you!\nYou made a list like this for Mei and the others!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5666585287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.6333011349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、思い出した！　芽衣、この沖縄のドーナツ\nだっていうサーターアンダギーが食べたかったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ I remember! I wanted to eat that\nOkinawan doughnut called sata andagi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "サーターアンダギーってなんかシャキーンって感じが\n必殺技みたいじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn't sata andagi sound like something special\nlike ta-da?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.2304869056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.499991862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……確かに昨日も言ってたよな。専門店が\n近くにあるみたいだし、俺で良ければ一緒に行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… You did say that yesterday. It seems there's\na specialty store nearby. If you're okay‚ I'll go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3999928792,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7099.995931100011,
          "startTime": 177.4999888103
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13333.329264399992,
          "startTime": 183.7333221436
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.166633451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_52_02-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　場所は……、わー、猫ちゃんだ！\nよしよーし。芽衣にすりすりしてきて、寂しいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! The location is… Wow‚ a kitty!\nGood‚ good. You're rubbing against Mei‚ maybe you are lonely?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7999888103,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16066.666666600015,
          "startTime": 197.8666554769
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
